title: Nalm6_Hmgn1_SE_HA_A1
characteristics_ch1.3: genotype: Nucleosome binding-deficient HMGN1 S20,24E mutant
treatment_protocol_ch1: HMGN1 expression induced by adding doxycycline (100ng/ml) or vehicle for six hours.
growth_protocol_ch1: RPMI + 10% FBS + 1% Penn/Strep/Glutamine at 37 degrees Celsius in 5% CO2
extract_protocol_ch1: Exactly one million cells were pelleted and total RNA was isolated using Trizol reagent. For per cell normalization, 1 μl of Mix #1 ERCC exogenous spike-in RNA (diluted 1:1000) was added to each RNA sample. Special attention was paid to equal and consistent volume transfers.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: TruSeq RNA Library Preparation Kit v2, Set A
description: Nucleosome binding-deficient HMGN1 S20,24E mutant, biological replicate A
data_processing.1: expression levels: Gene-level expression measurements for RefSeq genes were reported in fragments per kilobase per million reads (FPKM) by Cufflinks 2.0.0 (http://cufflinks.cbcb.umd.edu/) (Trapnell et al., 2010). Cufflinks assembles transcripts, estimates their abundance, and tests for differential expression and regulation in RNA-Seq samples. FPKM values were ERCC normalized. See methods for further details
data_processing.3: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: NALM6_all_fpkm_exprs_raw.txt: Tab-delimited text file matix containing raw FPKM values for each transcript; NALM6_all_fpkm_exprs_norm.txt:  Tab-delimited text file matix containing ERCC cell count normalized FPKM values for each transcript
